---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="lifeGLANCE"
  description="Your life, at a glance. lifeGLANCE is a personal milestone timeline. Zoom from a single week to multiple decades. Private, local, and offline-first."
  ogImage="/og/lifeglance.svg"
>
  <article class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="mb-10 font-sans text-sm text-glance-dim" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-glance-muted transition-colors">GLANCE Apps</a>
      <span class="mx-2">/</span>
      <span class="text-glance-muted">lifeGLANCE</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Left column -->
      <div>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold leading-none mb-4">
          <span class="text-glance-muted font-medium">life</span><span style="color: #7b70db;" class="tracking-wider font-bold">GLANCE</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-glance-muted font-serif italic mb-4">
          Your life, at a glance.
        </p>

        <img
          src="/glanceintents-pill-supports-purple-dark.svg"
          alt="Supports GLANCEintents"
          width="244"
          height="32"
          class="mb-8"
        />

        <div class="space-y-5 text-glance-muted font-serif text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          <p>
            lifeGLANCE is a zoomable personal timeline. Navigate your life's
            milestones in a view that can zoom from weeks to decades like zooming
            out on a map. Milestones appear on a continuous axis, anchored by
            today and groupable by Chapters. See the shape of your life at a glance.
          </p>
          <p>
            No goals to chase. No habits to streak. Just your life, laid out
            clearly, for you to navigate as you wish.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Platforms -->
        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-3">
            Platforms
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted mb-1">Web (lifeglance.app or self-host) · Android</p>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-dim mb-4">macOS · Windows · Linux · iOS (all coming soon)</p>
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-3">
            Languages
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted">English · French · German · Spanish · Italian · Portuguese · Chinese</p>
        </div>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mb-5">
          <a
            href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lifeglance.app"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="Get it on Google Play"
          >
            <img
              src="https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/badges/static/images/badges/en_badge_web_generic.png"
              alt="Get it on Google Play"
              width="155"
              height="60"
              class="h-[72px] w-auto"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6">
          <a
            href="/apps/lifeglance/downloads"
            class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted hover:text-[#7b70db] transition-colors duration-150"
          >
            All downloads →
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://lifeglance.app"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted hover:text-[#7b70db] transition-colors duration-150"
          >
            Visit lifeglance.app →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-5">
            What it does
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #7b70db;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Timeline navigation</strong>: Zoom from a single week to multiple decades. Past and future milestones sit side by side, with today always marked.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #7b70db;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Milestones</strong>: Add entries with titles, dates, categories, notes, and attachments. Photos, audio, and video all stored locally.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #7b70db;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Search and discovery</strong>: Full-text search, multiple views, a stats panel, and an "on this day" feature for anniversaries.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #7b70db;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Import and export</strong>: Import calendar files (.ics) in bulk. Export your timeline as a high-resolution image or JSON backup.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Cloud Sync -->
        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-4">
            Cloud Sync
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted leading-relaxed">
            Optional sync across your devices. No GLANCE Apps account. No GLANCE Apps servers. Zero-knowledge encrypted to a destination you control: WebDAV or Nextcloud. Off by default.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- GLANCEintents -->
        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-4">
            GLANCEintents
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted leading-relaxed">
            Designate milestones to track in dayGLANCE or receive goals from dayGLANCE. Bidirectional completion tracking. Off by default.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-10 section-rule">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-6">
        Open Source
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">
        lifeGLANCE is open source under the MIT License. Self-host the web app,
        build from source, or audit the code. Purchases on the app stores support
        continued development.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/krelltunez/lifeGLANCE"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-sans life-accent-link"
      >
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" class="shrink-0 opacity-75">
          <path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/>
        </svg>
        View on GitHub →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-10 section-rule">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-6">
        Privacy
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">
        lifeGLANCE stores your data locally on your device. No account required.
        No data leaves your device without your direction. Your data remains yours.
      </p>
      <a href="/privacy" class="font-sans text-sm life-accent-link">
        Privacy policy →
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .life-accent-link {
    color: #7b70db;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: #7b70db40;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 0.15s, text-decoration-color 0.15s;
  }
  .life-accent-link:hover {
    text-decoration-color: #7b70db;
  }
</style>
